        {
            "title": "比爾·蓋茲退出印度AI峰會主旨演講 基金會稱旨在確保會議聚焦核心議題",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 微軟公司聯合創始人比爾·蓋茲在即將發表演講前數小時，突然退出了這場備受矚目的印度<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>峰會主旨演講。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位億萬富翁的慈善機構蓋茲基金會解釋稱，此舉旨在確保會議焦點不受干擾，但未作進一步說明。在此次退出演講之前，他與已定罪性犯罪者傑弗裡·愛潑斯坦的關聯遭到批評，而且外界猜測這種關聯是否會威脅到該組織更廣泛的使命。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該基金會通過X平台發文稱，此舉是「經過慎重考慮後作出的決定，旨在確保人工智能峰會始終聚焦核心議題」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2d15eeae-b8f9-38d9-af81-a512a45028c9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蓋茲此前曾稱自己與愛潑斯坦的關係是「巨大錯誤」，並表示後悔曾多次與愛潑斯坦共進晚餐。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據英國《金融時報》報導，蓋茲基金會執行長Mark Suzman本月向員工表示，與愛潑斯坦的關聯已「玷污」了該組織的聲譽。除公開聲明外，該機構代表拒絕就蓋茲退出演講一事發表評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度人工智能峰會本周在新德里開幕，彰顯了總理納倫德拉·莫迪將這個世界人口最多國家打造為人工智能與科技強國的宏偉願景。蓋茲基金會印度與非洲事務負責人將代替蓋茲發言。微軟已經表示計畫向「全球南方」人工智能領域投資500億美元，以推動人工智能技術的普及。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bill Gates Pulls Out of India AI Summit Amid Epstein Criticism</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
