        {
            "title": "Alphabet VS Meta Platforms：哪一隻會稱霸未來10年？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t1.EqjOsfSlxDsusFTHDiA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/hk_moneyclub_713/9f2d14c3603a338205225abbfcb006fc\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Alphabet;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Alphabet\">Alphabet</a>（GOOGL、GOOG）及Meta Platforms（META）是互聯網時代的兩大巨頭，前者旗下的Google Search及YouTube、後者的多個社交媒體應用程式均極受歡迎，並為公司帶來可觀盈利。在這兩隻「MaginificentSeven」成員之中，哪一家公司更有機會在未來10年勝出？</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著互聯網用戶人數及使用時間持續增加，數碼廣告的「蛋糕」不斷做大，意味兩家公司在未來10年都將持續受惠。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-592dee78-2304-3920-aeec-756ac04c332b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">AI功能的引入，更可提升平台互動度及廣告投放的精準度；Alphabet在2025年收入按年增長15%，Meta則按年增長22%，兩家公司盈利能力均非常強勁，令其得以大量投資於AI相關資本開支。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">估值方面，Alphabet預測市盈率約28.8倍，Meta則更便宜，約22.5倍；投資者或可考慮兩者同時納入投資組合，因為兩家公司在未來盈利增長方面均具不俗潛力，股價在未來10年續創新高的機會頗大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作者：Neil Patel, The Fool</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 HKMoneyClub</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多你或感興趣內容：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:重溫「股壇長毛」David Webb的8大長線致勝法則;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/14/%e9%87%8d%e6%ba%ab%e3%80%8c%e8%82%a1%e5%a3%87%e9%95%b7%e6%af%9b%e3%80%8ddavid-webb%e7%9a%848%e5%a4%a7%e9%95%b7%e7%b7%9a%e8%87%b4%e5%8b%9d%e6%b3%95%e5%89%87/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">重溫「股壇長毛」David Webb的8大長線致勝法則</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:白銀2025年飆升144% 但歷史暗示2026年或大跌;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/28/%e7%99%bd%e9%8a%802025%e5%b9%b4%e9%a3%86%e5%8d%87144-%e4%bd%86%e6%ad%b7%e5%8f%b2%e6%9a%97%e7%a4%ba2026%e5%b9%b4%e6%88%96%e5%a4%a7%e8%b7%8c/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">白銀2025年飆升144% 但歷史暗示2026年或大跌</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:擔心AI泡沫爆破？這3種較穩陣的選擇可為投資組合提供防護;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyc