        {
            "title": "金價爆升 日本金筆議員徽章變套現神器？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tqOoz8247hkRBW7y2qK7Dw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/95a36580-0d59-11f1-8edf-239ddee5292b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金價創歷史新高，中環「忠記」日日有伯伯婆婆排隊賣金套現。原來日本亦有賣金套現潮，除了實金，只要有「含金量」的物品，例如金筆、假牙到議員徽章，都變成套現神器。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://yfinance.onelink.me/3068494570?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_[…]ub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub3=&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">鋼筆估值較預期高30倍</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據《朝日新聞》報道，隨著金價急升，一些含有黃金的日用品估值水漲船高。例如一枝舊鋼筆，放售的顧客預期只值100日圓，但因為筆嘴用金製造，二手店估值3000日圓，較預期回收價高30倍。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-eb0ca61a-7c9f-423d-aedd-7d1fa66ecdfd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑑定師解畫鋼筆的黃金筆嘴只有0.1或0.2克黃金，但金價高昂情況下，已足以推高回收價。除了鋼筆，只要含有黃金的日用品，如呔夾、袖口紐甚至用金製造的假牙，都可以用高價賣出套現。例如金牙，回收價可高見50萬日圓。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於一般人未必察覺收藏在家中的日用品會含有黃金，鑑定師鼓勵想套現的賣家可以到二手店先行鑑定，再判斷是否值得趁金價高企出售套現。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"金價高企更令東京都議員徽章成為另類套現神器。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qt8Di9oMTPzYw.rWuROOlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/2b880bf0-0d5a-11f1-bfd7-6e7f00e6c320\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">金價高企更令東京都議員徽章成為另類套現神器。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金價高企更令東京都議員徽章成為另類套現神器，這枚徽章因為含有黃金，網拍標價達34,100日圓，按金價計市價更達47,355日圓。為善用資源，據報熊本縣議會呼籲前議員交還舊徽章，成功回收132枚徽章，熔掉再製成金條進行拍賣，套現350萬日圓，今後則會改用鍍金徽章。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">逾3萬人入飛競逐「黃金糖」購買權</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金有價之下，黃金投資機會很容易掀起話題。大阪老牌糖果商吉寿屋於今年1月到3月，每月推出一件「黃金糖」以100萬日圓出售，吸引逾3萬人報名參與抽籤競逐認購權。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">能夠吸引不同年齡層顧客入飛認購「黃金糖」，關鍵原因是有水位可賺。按金價計算，「黃金糖」市值172.4萬日圓，水位足足有逾70萬日圓。而且這粒「黃金糖」數量有限，還有潛在的收藏升值價值。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%87%91%E5%83%B9%E7%88%86%E5%8D%87-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%87%91%E7%AD%86%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%BE%BD%E7%AB%A0%E8%AE%8A%E5%A5%97%E7%8F%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%9F-061758316.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-19 14:22:05",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
